@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: SVGTransform.java 980 2022-01-06 15:29:19Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.0.5") public static final class SVGTransform.SVGSkewY extends SVGTransform
The SVG skewY transformation.

This transformation definition specifies a skew transformation along the y-axis by a degrees. The operation corresponds to the matrix
      1    0  0
  ( tan a  1  0 )
      0    0  1
